<p style="color:blue"><b><i><u>php面向对象开发的学习</u></i></b></p><hr>	<?	class CMyClass	{		public $name;		public $age;				function CMyClass()		{			$this->name = "CMyClass()";			$this->age = 23;		}		function __construct($name="__construct()")		{			$this->name=$name;			$this->age = 24;			echo "I'm comming<br>";		}		function say()		{			return "我叫 $this->name , 我 $this->age 岁<br>";		}		function __destruct()		{			echo "销毁 $this->name<br>";		}	}		$My = new CMyClass();	echo $My->say();	$My = NULL;?><hr><p>	$this   $this->say();  $this->name;<br>  	初始化函数 __construct(){初始化操作} // 两条下划线<br>	析构函数 __destruct() // 类中指定对象释放时的动作<br>	</p><hr><p style="color:blue">封装</p><p>	public全局，内部外部，子类，都可以<br>	protected受保护的。本类或子类<br>	private私有的，本类内部<br>	<br>	__get()<br>	__set()<br></p><br><?	class CPersion	{		public $name = "mingzi";		protected $age = 23;		private $sex = "男";		public function say()		{			echo $this->name,"  ",$this->age,"    ",$this->sex,"<br>";		}		function __get($sex)		{			return $this->sex;		}		function __set($sex,$v)		{			$this->$sex=$v;		}			}		$my = new CPersion();		echo $my->name,"<br>";	//echo $my->age,"<br>";		$my->sex="女";	echo $my->sex,"<br>";	$my->say();	//$this->sex;	?><hr><p style="color:blue">继承 ：</p><p>	extends </p><?	class CPersions	{		public $eyes = 2;		private $hand = 2;		protected function say()		{			echo "Persion say<br>";		}	}		class CMan extends CPersions	{		/*		public function say()		{			echo "Man say<br>";		}		*/				public function say($str)		{			echo "Man say $str <br>";			CPersions::say();		}			}	$Man = new CMan();	$Man->say("Man");	echo $Man->eyes." eyes ";	//echo $Man->hand." hands <br>";?><hr><p style="color:red">	关键字:<br>	fianl 最终的<br>	self 用来用类访问当前类中的内容的关键字，可直接访问当前类中的内部成员<br>	static 可在类未在实例化时使用，静态属性单独占用内存，而不会因创建多个对象时而导致同样的方法或者属性重复占用，里面禁止使用非静态内容<br>	const 用来定义类中的常量，类似外部定义常量define(); 建立大写的常量  常量是不需要"$"的<br></p><hr size=10 color=red><p style="color:green;background:red">接口：</p><p>	关键字：<br>		interface 声明接口<br>		implements 用于引用接口 可一次引用多个接口，用逗号分隔<br>		</p><hr><p style="color:red;background:yellow"><b>多态</b></p><p></p>